title: Changed delay time on logger
description: Weather station Cahto Peak had incorrect delay time after powering up sensors for measuring barometric pressure.  Delay time was too short at 150 milliseconds.  It is now 1 second.   Period affected:  12/8/2009 16:45 to 1/8/2010 14:30 Comments:[1/11/2010 Ginger] Flagged 38,558 datavalues where station is Cahto Peak and LocalDateTime > '2009-12-08 16:45' and LocalDateTime < '2010-01-08 14:30:00' incident report migrated from SensorDB.

external_refs.identifier: Passed sanity check; see incident report IR_7
